[normal]8 October 2013
[normal]The UK Food and Drink Manufacturing Industry[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]The Food and Drink Federation (FDF) rep
[normal]resents the food and drink manufacturing industry, the largest manufacturing sector in the UK, employing 400,000 people.  The industry has an annual turnover of over £76bn accounting 
[normal]for 15% of the total manufacturing sector.  Exports amount to over £12bn 
[normal]of which 77% goes to EU members. The industry buys two-thirds of all UK’s agricultural produce.
[normal]&#xa0;
